Telepathic Link (Ex)		KEY:Telepathic Link ~ Ambush Drake	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.AmbushDrake Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Ambush drakes share a communal consciousness, enabling them to communicate telepathically with other ambush drakes. A group of ambush drakes within 30 feet of each other are in constant contact. If one is aware of a particular danger, they all are. If one in the group is not flat-footed, none of them are. No ambush drake in the group is considered flanked unless all are.																		SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Skills				KEY:Skills ~ Ambush Drake		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.AmbushDrake Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Ambush drakes have a +4 racial bonus on Hide checks.																																																																		BONUS:SKILL|Hide|4|TYPE=Racial	SOURCEPAGE:p.88

